上饶站货场位于普速场北侧，办理整车普通货物到发业务。货场北侧为上饶国际物流中心，又稱“无水港”，驻有上饶铁路口岸。货场每天有发往[[宁波舟山港|宁波舟山港]]的海铁联运列车<ref>{{cite news|title = 上饶-宁波“海铁联运天天班”正式开通|url = http://kab.sh.gov.cn/zmhd/005004/005004004/20140527/9c0e214c-61b6-41c9-ba42-47b9f9e2185e.html|publisher = 上海市商务委|date = 2014-05-27|access-date = 2019-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190923055844/http://kab.sh.gov.cn/zmhd/005004/005004004/20140527/9c0e214c-61b6-41c9-ba42-47b9f9e2185e.html|archive-date = 2019-09-23|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，2018年开通至[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]的[[中欧班列|中欧班列]]<ref>{{cite web|title = 上饶国际物流中心|url = http://218.87.46.162/indexInfo/indexPic/indexSrgl.jsp|publisher = 江西电子口岸|access-date = 2019-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190923055844/http://218.87.46.162/indexInfo/indexPic/indexSrgl.jsp|archive-date = 2019-09-23|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title = 上饶首列中欧班列正式发车|url = http://jx.ifeng.com/a/20180122/6324350_0.shtml|work = 中国江西网-江西日报|publisher = 凤凰网|date = 2018-01-22|accessdate = 2019-09-23|archive-date = 2019-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190923055842/http://jx.ifeng.com/a/20180122/6324350_0.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。货场设有通往[[中石化|中石化]]灵溪油库、上饶材料厂、[[鹰潭机务段|鹰潭机务段]]上饶运用车间和鹰潭工务段上饶材料分库的专用线<ref name="95306info">{{cite web|url = http://hyfw.95306.cn/hyinfo/action/FwcszsAction_index?type=1|title = 营业站服务信息查询|publisher = 中国铁路95306网|accessdate = 2019-09-23|archive-date = 2018-09-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180914133603/http://hyfw.95306.cn/hyinfo/action/FwcszsAction_index?type=1|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

